  array(
    'username',
    'password',
    'mytable.region as region',
    'firstname'
  )
);
</code></pre>

<p>In the example above, the 'firstname' column is treated as "mytable"."firstname", as though the usage of "mytable.region" in the preceding array element causes following columns to use that table name as well.</p>

